<h3>27 September 2020 - SimpleBlogScript</h3>

<p>This is <a href="https://www.haywalk.ca">haywalk</a>'s blog script. The code can be found <a href="https://github.com/haywalk/simpleblogscript">here</a>.</p>

<p><b>Steps to posting:</b> To post to this blog, add a plaintext file (with no *.txt ending), and name it <code>###-DDmonthYYYY</code>, where <code>###</code> is the post number (your first post should be 1, etc.), <code>DD</code> is the day (numerical), <code>month</code> is the month (written/lowercase), and <code>YYYY</code> is the year (numerical). Then, you simply write your post out in HTML in your post file!</p>
